author: Vaibhav  Pratap

text:
Kuch to log kahengeâ€¦ Logon ka kaam hai kahna.
Same with me, yaar tu nahi to college kaafi khaali khaali hota. Tujhe follow karte karte photography kar li(thoda utkarsh ke karan bhi). Tere hi kaaran galaxy aur antaragni kar li and most important nashedi bhi tere karan bana(tere alawa aur koi iske liye aisa motivate kar hi nahi sakta tha). Matlab ye sab agar mere life me nahi hota to pata nahi college life ka kya hota.
First year ke baad jab room allocation ho raha tha, mai tere se roomie banne ke liye puch nahi pa raha tha, mujhe lag raha tha ki tune kisi aur ke saath plan kar liya hoga? But andar se feeling aa rahi thi ki apni bond next level banegi and see nowâ€¦. I was right.
Ek bhi birthday me IIT me nahi tha, lekin tujhe gift jaroor chahiye, waah!!  Raat ki parties aur wo luv stories(waise kaafi sahi jodi hai teri,"KAAFI"), Pata nahi mai kitne saare bet haara hoon tujhjse, lucky you, dinner ek saath karna, dp bhi saath change karna, Galaxy saath jeetna, unscheduled movies show, tujhse taash me haarna(ek bas tu hi hai jiske opposite mere  stats kharab hai yaar) aur haan ab room ke lights to mere hi honge...........
Bhut hi jyada shandaar tha college and you were almost in every beautiful memory. I can't imagine IIT without you. Ye sab to mai aise hi likh raha, as you know mujhe likhna nahi aata leki fir bhi you should know that you are very very special to me.
Until next time,
PRATI
author: Vaibhav  Pratap

text: Remember the time when we were managers in the design team, and working at hall 12, Mukul and Garvit were talking about your beautiful posters, and this was the first time I came to know about you(waise to hum wingy hain but utni jaan pahchaan nahi thi), and I felt jealous, then I saw your works, and it was very awesome. Then one day we were working together, and I asked for your help, and you did it very gladly. From that day to the last day of Antaragni, I loved working with you. Thanks buddy, for all the laugh and fun and keep encouraging me.
author: Vaibhav  Pratap

text:
IIT ka pahla friend, so special to hona hi tha. Chicken khane ka craze, Raat me campus ghoomna, OAT me pizza khana, apne photography ke liye mujhe model banana, Gym ke liye inspire karna, Galaxy jeetna... sab kaafi majedaar tha.
GPL ke liye room se aadhi neend me chappal lekar nikalna, bhand hoke pronite ground par roll hona, hall cultural program me stand up comedy karna(jisme sirf tujhe hi hasi aa rahi hai), tinder per match par match aana.... wo bhi kya din the.

-PRATI
author: Vaibhav  Pratap

text: I thought it wouldn't be okay to write but now I think it is very okay. Ce ke lab ki backchodiyan hamesha yaad rahengi,especially techkriti head "vipul". Bhai tumhare aur sonkar ke  kaaran, labs lab nahi fun lagne lage the and actually mai lab ka wait karne laga tha ki kab lab hongi aur fir wahan backchodi karenge.  Aur bhai hall me aakar canteen lekar jaaana ye to sabse jyada yaad rahega but ab treat dene ki baari aapki hai. It is good to have you <3.
author: Vaibhav  Pratap
